OL,3,C'Sickening and deplorable': Attack on
OL,4,Cbusiness 'racist'
OL,6,FA racist attack on at County Antrim
OL,7,Fbusiness has been condemned by local
OL,8,Frepresentatives.
OL,10,FAn Indian-Nepalese restaurant in
OL,11,FNewtownabbey was set alight and racist
OL,12,Fgraffiti sprayed on a wall in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Wednesday, 21 August.
OL,15,FPolice received a report of arson
OL,16,Fwhich is thought to have occurred at
OL,17,Fthe licensed premises in the
OL,18,FBallyclare Road area.
