OL,6,FParts of the Ballyclare Road were
OL,7,Fclosed as firefighters dealt with the
OL,8,Fblaze.
OL,10,FIn a statement issued on Wednesday,
OL,11,Fthe PSNI confirmed that the incident
OL,12,Fwas deliberate and is being treated as
OL,13,Fa racially-motivated hate crime.
OL,15,FSinn Fein MP John Finucane described
OL,16,Fthe attack as 'sickening and
OL,17,Fdeplorable'.
