OL,3,C'Sickening and deplorable': Attack on
OL,4,Cbusiness 'racist'
OL,6,F"Those intent on causing hate and
OL,7,Fstirring up division must face the
OL,8,Ffull force of the law, and I would
OL,9,Fappeal to anyone who may have
OL,10,Finformation on this incident to bring
OL,11,Fit forward to police."
OL,13,FMLA Pam Cameron also condemned the
OL,14,Fattack.
OL,16,FThe DUP MLA said "This was an attack
OL,17,Fon a local business. There can be no
OL,18,Fjustification for attacking any
OL,19,Fproperty and particularly for the
OL,20,Fsinister graffiti that was sprayed
OL,21,Fonto the building.
