OL,3,C'Sickening and deplorable': Attack on
OL,4,Cbusiness 'racist'
OL,6,F"The owners of the restaurant have
OL,7,Fbeen working hard to build up their
OL,8,Fbusiness and contribute to the local
OL,9,Fcommunity. Their efforts are a world
OL,10,Faway from those with nothing to offer
OL,11,Fbut hate, destruction and chaos.
OL,13,F"We will continue to stand with all
OL,14,Fthose who want to build a better
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, and particularly
OL,16,Fwith those who feel fearful because of
OL,17,Frecent attacks such as this."
