OL,3,C'Sickening and deplorable': Attack on
OL,4,Cbusiness 'racist'
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Crothers added: "At
OL,7,Faround 1.50am, it was reported that a
OL,8,Fproperty was set alight in the area.
OL,9,FGraffiti was also reported on the
OL,10,Fpremises following the incident.
OL,12,F"Colleagues from Northern Ireland Fire
OL,13,F& Rescue Service attended and dealt
OL,14,Fwith the fire, which is being treated
OL,15,Fas deliberate ignition.
OL,17,F"Enquiries are continuing and at this
OL,18,Fstage, the incident is being treated
OL,19,Fas a racially motivated hate crime."
